title: Jan. 6 House Panel Issues 11 More Subpoenas in Connection With Capitol Riot
sub_head: Select Committee is seeking documents and testimony from people allegedly involved in organizing pro-Trump rally on Jan. 6 prior to attack
body:
WASHINGTONâ€”A House Select Committee has issued 11 subpoenas for documents and testimony from people allegedly involved in planning the Jan. 6 rally at the Ellipse before supporters of former President Donald Trump attacked the U.S. Capitol.
The panel already has issued subpoenas to four former Trump administration officials.
